snippet.title: Thirty Cycles - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Playing my Nemesis Jam entry game.

Intentionally picked a very difficult start and spent most of the game trying to catch up. Assassinated a top-level character at like cycle 10, managed to catch up to lowest levels, then picked favorable fights and had a few successful gambles. The last two cycles were really intense, I've got assassinated a few times, a 2nd highest level character was always in danger of assassinating me, so I had to stay away from it.

But in the end, I won! Yay.

Get Thirty Cycles from Itch.io:
https://zuurix.itch.io/thirty-cycles
